Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.95,0:00:09.27,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right! Now let's move forward
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.29,0:00:12.65,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,with the sun always in our hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.67,0:00:16.07,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,As power passes through our clasped hands
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.09,0:00:24.09,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,let's grab hold of our wishes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.22,0:00:34.75,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Working together, let's ride the giant waves
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.77,0:00:41.93,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry toward the excitement--\Nthere's the starting signal
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.95,0:00:48.89,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Now's the time to set sail-- let's raise anchor
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.91,0:00:56.02,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut through the rainbow-colored wind\Nand head for a sea of adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.04,0:00:59.53,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be a journey fraught with injury
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.55,0:01:03.41,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,but what you cherish most will be right there
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.43,0:01:07.41,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And if you get into a jam
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.43,0:01:10.41,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll always be there to protect you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.43,0:01:14.63,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right! Now let's move forward
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.65,0:01:18.13,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,with the sun always in our hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.15,0:01:21.13,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If a storm hits, let's put\Nour arms around each other
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.15,0:01:25.64,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and gaze at the light beyond
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.66,0:01:29.35,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If we gather up the pieces of our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.37,0:01:32.64,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,they'll make a map leading to tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.66,0:01:35.65,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's grab hold of our wishes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.67,0:01:41.44,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,under the same flag-- together, we're one
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.46,0:01:49.46,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,One Piece
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.89,0:01:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Team Foxy wins yet again in the\Nsecond round of this second fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.81,0:01:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you've lost two crewmates.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.65,0:02:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One game remains, and you can only\Ntake back one crew member at most.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.74,0:02:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, even if you do beat me in this next game,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.03,0:02:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you've already lost one crewmate for good!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.00,0:02:21.00,B1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2000,2000)}"The Captains Square Off!\NThe Final Combat Round!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.96,0:02:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, Boss!\NChoose your bounty, if you please!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.31,0:02:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the second one I choose!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.65,0:02:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Choppy! I won't leave you ever again!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.99,0:02:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.03,0:02:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't cry, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.41,0:02:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, things are looking pretty bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.91,0:02:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are we gonna do, Luffy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.42,0:03:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry! We'll just do\Nanother Davy Back Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.67,0:03:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Another one?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.92,0:03:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.26,0:03:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, shall I tell you why we Foxy Pirates\Nare known as the mightiest of all?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.18,0:03:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Heh. Says they're the mightiest.\N--After losing to us twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.39,0:03:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.02,0:03:23.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We had five three-coin games
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.11,0:03:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with the Fang-Frog Pirates\Ntoday before we ran into you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.90,0:03:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Many of us are hurt. We're exhausted,\Nboth mentally and physically...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.33,0:03:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're ready to call it quits.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.37,0:03:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we won't agree to any more fights,\Nhowever much you want one!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.33,0:03:46.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Knowing when enough is enough--\Nwhen it's time to quit--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.55,0:03:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is why we're the mightiest!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.30,0:03:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why aren't you saying anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.81,0:03:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.77,0:04:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Acting like you're the\Nunderdogs here... Are you an idiot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.15,0:04:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that what you call the "mightiest crew"?\NWhat a bunch of Peanut crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.61,0:04:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you be so laid-back?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.12,0:04:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't choose between Chopper and Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.54,0:04:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are we just gonna let 'em keep 'em?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.70,0:04:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be stupid! I'm gonna get both back!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.79,0:04:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And how do you plan to do that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.58,0:04:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a pain. Maybe I\Nshould just chop 'em all up...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.92,0:04:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uhh, this is a game, you know. A game...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.80,0:04:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, "Boss"! I have an offer...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.39,0:04:39.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.18,0:04:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you say we bet\Nfive people on the next game?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.31,0:04:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey, now! You can't just decide--!\N--No, let's leave this to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.53,0:04:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come again?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.61,0:04:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This game is all about taking\Ncrew members you want, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.28,0:04:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we want those two!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.12,0:04:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no point to this if\Nwe can't get 'em both back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.24,0:04:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.54,0:05:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, if we win the next game,\Nyou'll give them back to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.88,0:05:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if you win, all five of us\Nwill join your crew too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.92,0:05:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you say? It's a pretty\Ngood deal if you ask me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.43,0:05:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This girl has some serious guts\Nto try and bargain with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.76,0:05:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those two clearly have enormous power...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.93,0:05:25.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This one and his strange\Nimplements could be useful...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.27,0:05:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And most valuable of all is this\Nguy worth 100 million Berries!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.24,0:05:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Two is way too cheap, though!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.41,0:05:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bet 500 people!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.58,0:05:44.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you win, I'll give you 500 people,\Nincluding those two!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.33,0:05:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha...? Why 500?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.21,0:05:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my! Our boss has made\Nthe "Hellish 500-Man Wager!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.96,0:05:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will Straw Hat accept?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.55,0:05:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't need 500 people!\NAre you stupid or something?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.51,0:05:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.55,0:06:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're so close to making a deal!\NDon't back out now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.43,0:06:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Merry can't carry 500 people!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.77,0:06:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Getting Chopper and Robin-chan\Nback is all that matters!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.40,0:06:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Five or 500, it makes no difference!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.31,0:06:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.73,0:06:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you accept?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.40,0:06:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.32,0:06:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Incidentally, should the losing\Nteam not have 500 people,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.32,0:06:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the remainder will be made up\Nby the team's descendants.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.53,0:06:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, your children,\Ngrandchildren, and great-grandchildren
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.66,0:06:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will be forced to swear loyalty to\Nthe Foxy Pirates until the total is met!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.05,0:06:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Children...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.43,0:06:36.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.93,0:06:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.93,0:06:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've suddenly added a\Nstrange condition to the mix...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.02,0:06:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have much of a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.10,0:06:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just have to win! Understand, Luffy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.86,0:06:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.73,0:06:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nice that you're raring to go and all,\Nbut I should warn you now
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.86,0:06:59.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that it's impossible to beat me\Nin the final combat round.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.49,0:07:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I suggest you all ready yourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.49,0:07:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! I'd never lose to you in a fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.29,0:07:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many times must I repeat myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.42,0:07:18.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A fight and a game are two different things...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.05,0:07:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Foxy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.06,0:07:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At last, it's time for the final combat round!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.39,0:07:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First order of business:\Nestablishing the battlefield!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.81,0:07:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The two competitors spin the cannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.19,0:07:32.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.73,0:07:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...wherever it stops will be where--!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.44,0:07:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on! That was clearly not normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.66,0:07:44.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The battlefield has been set!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.08,0:07:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By sheer coincidence, it's on\Nthe deck of our own Sexy Foxy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.50,0:07:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coincidence, my butt! You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.04,0:07:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll now explain the rules of combat!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.50,0:07:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything within 50 meters\Nof where the cannonball landed
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.97,0:07:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is part of the battlefield!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.72,0:08:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, it's a 100-meter-wide circle!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.89,0:08:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weapons are allowed, as well as\Nanything else within the circle!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.85,0:08:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only the two competitors\Nare allowed inside the circle!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.73,0:08:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Knock your opponent out of\Nthe circle and you win! That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.57,0:08:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Note that the air and water inside\Nthe circle still counts as in-bounds!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.99,0:08:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,F! O! X! Y!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.99,0:08:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Foxy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.87,0:08:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Flower Cheerleaders\Nare currently on the stage
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.50,0:08:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,performing cheers for our boss,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.33,0:08:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,while an opening fight is\Nbeing held aboard the Foxy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.17,0:08:36.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Additionally, the Association of Stalls
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.50,0:08:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is selling limited-edition\NDavy Back Fight merchandise,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.47,0:08:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so be sure to check them out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.18,0:08:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't need any of this! Just get started!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.51,0:08:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--...please!\N--Okay! Limited-edition Foxy pins!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.51,0:08:47.41,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"Foxy Pins"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.43,0:08:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't buy their junk!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.02,0:08:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Excuse me. Where's the participant...?\N--There! Just take him already!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.36,0:08:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you so mad about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.15,0:09:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh! Why isn't anyone taking this seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.03,0:09:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It really ticks me off how their boss\Nis dictating the pace of everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.78,0:09:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I dunno, it's probably just 'cause\Nthey've gained so many crew members...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.87,0:09:12.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They clearly have more than enough now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.04,0:09:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All that matters is that Luffy wins, Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.50,0:09:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go buy us some drinks! Go on ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.80,0:09:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you two! Come on over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.76,0:09:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here! For you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.77,0:09:33.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--How much is it?\N--It's on the house!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.19,0:09:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.90,0:09:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah! Even if Luffy loses,\Nthey'll all be part of this team too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.65,0:09:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't have to go our separate ways!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.45,0:09:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if that happens, Captain\Nwon't be our captain anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.08,0:09:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll all be serving under a new boss...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.21,0:10:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--The King of the Pirates...\N--...will be me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.80,0:10:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys better work hard for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.26,0:10:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.97,0:10:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Luffy's going to win, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.23,0:10:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All seven of us are gonna get\Nto continue our journey, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.77,0:10:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's pray it turns out that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.82,0:10:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?! Why does popcorn\Nand a cola cost so much?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.33,0:10:34.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't like it, don't buy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.58,0:10:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Lower it 80%!\N--Get outta my face!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.34,0:10:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is all this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.84,0:10:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the dressing room.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.71,0:10:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a gloved fight, so choose anything you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.18,0:10:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.10,0:10:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, this is more like a costume\Nroom than a dressing room...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.77,0:11:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at all this stuff! And I can\Nuse anything I want, Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.86,0:11:07.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, how about this? Does it look good?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.45,0:11:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... This is it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.70,0:11:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The boundaries are in place!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.50,0:11:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This ends the opening entertainment!\NThank you for your patience!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.75,0:11:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now for today's main event...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.71,0:11:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Combat! The bell will ring shortly!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.85,0:11:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry to the spectator stands, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.43,0:11:36.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.93,0:11:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sky is turning dark...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.11,0:11:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san! Where are you?! Say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.24,0:11:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch where you're walkin', crappy cook.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.54,0:12:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This time we're being treated to\Na captain-versus-captain battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.13,0:12:04.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Beat 'im up, Boss!\N--We're counting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.55,0:12:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, in the left figurehead corner...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.13,0:12:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A man who takes on all challengers
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.30,0:12:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and boasts a legendary, undefeated\Nrecord of 920 wins and 0 losses!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.10,0:12:18.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.56,0:12:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our boss, Silver Fox Foxy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.86,0:12:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.36,0:12:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up, Luffy. You ain't your old self no more.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.49,0:12:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That hairstyle arouses a man's true wildness.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.50,0:12:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some ask if the champion makes the afro,\Nor if the afro makes the champion...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.42,0:12:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not even modern science can explain it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.46,0:12:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy... With an afro on, your punches\Nwill have some serious firepower.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.05,0:12:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Where's Straw Hat?!\N--Did he wimp out on us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.93,0:12:59.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it, Pops.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.85,0:13:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.27,0:13:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And in the right corner, hailing from East Blue!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.23,0:13:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The leader of a miniscule pirate band\Nwith a 100 million-Berry bounty...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.70,0:13:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,..."Straw Hat" Monkey D. Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.58,0:13:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! The afroed Luffy is all\Nfired up in the right corner!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.34,0:13:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lookin' sharp, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.42,0:13:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you kidding me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.55,0:13:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy looks so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.93,0:13:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He certainly does.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.18,0:13:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both fighters have stepped onto the battlefield!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.89,0:13:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can Straw Hat successfully\Nknock our boss out of the circle
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.52,0:13:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and protect his crew and pride?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.11,0:13:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or will our boss's legendary undefeated\Nstreak strip him of everything he has?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.03,0:13:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This final and fateful combat\Nround of the Davy Back Fight
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.03,0:13:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is about to begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.24,0:14:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But first, a word from our sponsors.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.27,0:14:27.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Straw Hat! Nice fashion!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.23,0:14:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your butt is as good as kicked!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.65,0:14:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep your arms tucked in and\Nshow 'im your golden right punch!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.69,0:14:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.24,0:14:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! His brotherly soul is burning red-hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.62,0:14:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Letting Usopp be his corner man was a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.12,0:14:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish he'd take this seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.54,0:14:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Not too shabby!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.25,0:14:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a wild style!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.50,0:14:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quite admirable, even if you are my opponent!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.55,0:14:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't act so confident\Nif I were you, Champion!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.93,0:14:59.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's liable to bite your head off!\NBetter watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.51,0:15:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, corner man! You're in the way! Scram!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.77,0:15:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! My job as corner man is over already?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.52,0:15:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Corner man, out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.10,0:15:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get goin' already!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.69,0:15:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're absolutely right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.48,0:15:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need for me to remain\Nhere either! I'll leave as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.28,0:15:21.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? The stands are...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.83,0:15:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, cool! I didn't know they did that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.71,0:15:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, Straw Hat Luffy.\NLet's have some fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.80,0:15:38.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This entire ship is our battlefield!\NRampage to your heart's desire!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.43,0:15:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have plenty of skilled shipwrights, you see!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.64,0:15:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By sheer luck, this bout is taking\Nplace aboard the Sexy Foxy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.19,0:15:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of deadly struggle\Nis about to unfold?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.36,0:15:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The two pirates are now all alone\Ninside the spacious battlefield!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.36,0:16:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Boss!\N--Keep your undefeated streak going!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.32,0:16:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Win, Luffy! You hafta win!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.24,0:16:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His beam! Watch out for his beam!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.66,0:16:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excitement fills the stands!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.21,0:16:12.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's plunder or be plundered!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.38,0:16:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,500 people are on the line in this final\Ncombat round of the Davy Back Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.30,0:16:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's one match only, with no time limit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.22,0:16:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Luffy!\N--Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.22,0:16:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Silver Fox Foxy versus Straw Hat Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.97,0:16:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a head-to-head battle between\Nthese two pirate powerhouses!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.39,0:16:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fate of everything hangs in the balance!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.77,0:16:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here comes...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.52,0:16:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the starting bell!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.11,0:16:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Let's do it!\N--Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.69,0:16:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Gum-Gum... Pistol!\N--Slow-Slow Beam!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.91,0:16:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only my fist is slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.96,0:16:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not so tough! You're all show!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.88,0:16:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.63,0:17:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.01,0:17:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Slow-Slow...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.93,0:17:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.01,0:17:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.06,0:17:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.56,0:17:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Slow-Slow Beam!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.10,0:17:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.61,0:17:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's floating! He's slow even when falling?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.69,0:17:24.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told him to watch out for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.95,0:17:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about lame!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.58,0:17:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now beat 'im, Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.70,0:17:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aww... Crap...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.54,0:17:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Straw Hat?\NReady to throw in the towel already?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.84,0:17:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.64,0:17:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...what...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.64,0:17:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nine-Tails Rush!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.68,0:17:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Our boss unleashes a\Nfierce attack right off the bat!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.15,0:18:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat is helpless to do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.86,0:18:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? He isn't even budging...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.24,0:18:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.66,0:18:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The effects are slow too, that's all!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.79,0:18:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was just a little "hello."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.05,0:18:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The punches themselves\Ndidn't hurt you too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.34,0:18:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That much is obvious to me, rubber man!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.93,0:18:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn... it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.47,0:18:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, your thirty seconds are about up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.48,0:18:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It's hitting him all at once!\N--Oh, no! He's going overboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.86,0:18:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.24,0:18:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap! The Slow-Slow Beam is\Nmore dangerous than I thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.62,0:18:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beams sure are nice...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.83,0:18:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess I shouldn't stretch more than I need to...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.42,0:19:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd that jerk go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.76,0:19:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! I won't get hit by that anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.43,0:19:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come out, Split-Head!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.22,0:19:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't take your anger out on the ears!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.06,0:19:24.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Another Slow-Slow?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.65,0:19:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to my ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.28,0:19:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.57,0:19:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He got me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.78,0:19:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.33,0:19:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm trying to show you some hospitality here...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.17,0:19:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those cannonballs have been Slow-Slow-ed...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.17,0:19:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can ride one, then I can too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.92,0:19:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...! I wouldn't ride that one if I were you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.18,0:19:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, or that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.98,0:20:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Told you so!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.23,0:20:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this? What's going on in the fight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.07,0:20:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.24,0:20:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you see anything from up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.62,0:20:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing but smoke!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.92,0:20:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.59,0:20:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, he's wrecking his own ship...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.18,0:20:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just getting started!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.80,0:20:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Slow-Slow Foxy Face Bombs!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.73,0:20:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Freaky!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.98,0:20:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Pin badges? They're\Nbigger than the one I bought!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.86,0:20:51.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course we are! We're bombs!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.24,0:20:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are?! Yikes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.53,0:20:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? A bomb just talked!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.08,0:21:01.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... the real deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.37,0:21:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Straw Hat...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.00,0:21:05.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I upgraded my gloves!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.75,0:21:12.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the Face Bombs'\N30 seconds are just about up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.93,0:21:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah! Luffy! The body! The body!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.89,0:21:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.56,0:21:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's happening with the fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.06,0:21:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dunno. Beats me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.23,0:21:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.83,0:21:45.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy... Oh, no...!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.15,0:22:09.25,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,A piece of a dream that we started grasping
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.27,0:22:12.80,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Chasing after something constant
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.82,0:22:18.39,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We send our aspirations sailing into the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.41,0:22:20.68,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Even when we're exhausted
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.70,0:22:23.85,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We have a compass that can\Nsearch for something constant
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.87,0:22:29.27,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, do you think we can keep it forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.29,0:22:32.19,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,At the end of the dream\Nthat we will reach someday
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.21,0:22:35.07,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We want to be adults as we\Nare now as much as possible
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.09,0:22:37.95,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We pray to this endless sky that we look up at
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.97,0:22:40.99,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Eternally... Eternally...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.01,0:22:43.83,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Wild fantasies from our childhood
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.85,0:22:46.63,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We trace unforgettable memories
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.65,0:22:52.34,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And try to keep the embers\Nburning that still consume us
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.36,0:22:55.09,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,To this familiar sunny sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.11,0:22:57.97,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Together we entrust our feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.99,0:23:00.56,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We go beyond the changing time
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.58,0:23:08.58,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Eternally... Eternally...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.13,0:23:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get up! Get up, Joe-- err, come on, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.76,0:23:16.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Do a No-Guard stance, then a double-cross!\N--Who are you pretending to be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.63,0:23:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now! Remember the eye of the tig--!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.18,0:23:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not you too, Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.89,0:23:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Pops... I'm gonna be pure white ash...\N--Don't burn up! Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.98,0:23:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm having fun! Come on, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.77,0:23:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.98,0:23:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Full-Blast Slow-Slow Onslaught\Nvs. Invulnerable Luffy"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.65,0:23:32.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I'm gonna be King of--\N--Nope, I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.48,0:23:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
